unite-sorce for BEAR (inspired by unite-rails)

Usage:
  Unite bear/App
    : BEAR_HOME/App/

  Unite bear/htdocs
    : BEAR_HOME/htdocs/

  Unite bear/libs
    : BEAR_HOME/libs/

  Unite bear/Form
    : BEAR_HOME/App/Form

  Unite bear/Page
    : BEAR_HOME/App/Page/

  Unite bear/Ro
    : BEAR_HOME/App/Ro/

  Unite bear/views
    : BEAR_HOME/App/views/


Key Map example.

nnoremap <silent> uba :<C-u>UniteWithInput bear/App<CR>
nnoremap <silent> ubr :<C-u>UniteWithInput bear/Ro<CR>
nnoremap <silent> ubv :<C-u>UniteWithInput bear/views<CR>
nnoremap <silent> ubp :<C-u>UniteWithInput bear/Page<CR>
nnoremap <silent> ubh :<C-u>UniteWithInput bear/htdocs<CR>
nnoremap <silent> ubl :<C-u>UniteWithInput bear/libs<CR>
nnoremap <silent> ubf :<C-u>UniteWithInput bear/Form<CR>

